1
00:03:51,355 --> 00:03:53,289
<font color="#00ff00">Oke, para gadis.</font>

2
00:03:58,795 --> 00:04:01,697
<font color="#00ff00">Ya Tuhan, tempat ini membuatku merinding.</font>

3
00:04:01,699 --> 00:04:03,598
<font color="#00ff00">Di mana yang menakutkannya?</font>

4
00:04:03,600 --> 00:04:04,566
<font color="#00ff00">Di sana.</font>

5
00:04:05,768 --> 00:04:07,702
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Kalian punya waktu 20 menit.</i></font>

6
00:04:07,704 --> 00:04:08,703
<font color="#00ff00">Terserah.</font>

7
00:04:22,817 --> 00:04:24,984
<font color="#00ff00">Whoa, whoa, whoa!</font>

8
00:04:26,455 --> 00:04:27,820
<font color="#00ff00">Sial.</font>

9
00:04:28,221 --> 00:04:30,222
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Semuanya baik saja?</i></font>

10
00:04:32,926 --> 00:04:35,661
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Semua baik saja.
Kami datang.</i></font>

11
00:05:00,550 --> 00:05:01,617
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Oke.</i></font>

12
00:05:01,852 --> 00:05:04,487
<font color="#00ff00">Ya, ke arahku.
Bagus, sudah kupegang.</font>

13
00:05:04,821 --> 00:05:07,055
<font color="#00ff00">Tunggu.
Bagus.</font>

14
00:05:07,289 --> 00:05:08,356
<font color="#00ff00">Sudah?</font>

15
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:12,200
<font color="#00ff00">Ayo terus, terus. /
Tahan!</font>

16
00:05:12,995 --> 00:05:14,496
<font color="#00ff00">Baiklah, aku memegangnya.</font>

17
00:05:15,097 --> 00:05:16,830
<font color="#00ff00">Pelan-pelan.
Dengan lembut.</font>

18
00:05:39,685 --> 00:05:43,955
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Harap tetap berada di kursi anda dan
kencangkan sabuk pengaman anda.</i></font>

19
00:05:43,957 --> 00:05:45,357
<font color="#00ff00">Astaga!</font>

20
00:05:45,858 --> 00:05:48,192
<font color="#00ff00">Aku tahu perasaanmu, Nak.
Terbang?</font>

21
00:05:48,460 --> 00:05:51,529
<font color="#00ff00">Terbang dulu juga membuatku sangat takut.</font>

22
00:05:51,863 --> 00:05:53,297
<font color="#00ff00">Ayo.</font>

23
00:05:53,299 --> 00:05:57,867
<font color="#00ff00">Aku sering bepergian dan kuberitahu,
memacu mobil Civic di jalan alternatif,</font>

24
00:05:58,068 --> 00:06:00,670
<font color="#00ff00">itu sudah tak berguna.
Kau tahu maksudku, kan?</font>

25
00:06:01,672 --> 00:06:04,274
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Tuan dan nyonya sekalian,
kita akan mendarat</i></font>

26
00:06:04,575 --> 00:06:06,442
<font color="#00ff00"><i>sesuai jadwal di Chicago O'Hare.</i></font>

27
00:06:06,710 --> 00:06:09,044
<font color="#00ff00">Apa kita mendarat?
/ Tentu saja kita mendarat.</font>

28
00:06:09,046 --> 00:06:10,846
<font color="#00ff00">Tempat ini dibangun untuk itu.</font>

29
00:06:10,848 --> 00:06:12,614
<font color="#00ff00">Aku kacau.</font>

30
00:06:13,950 --> 00:06:15,417
<font color="#00ff00">Permisi?</font>

31
00:06:16,419 --> 00:06:18,286
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Apa yang kauharapkan, Tom?</i></font>

32
00:06:18,554 --> 00:06:20,087
<font color="#00ff00">Entahlah. Yang berhubungan dengan Chicago.</font>

33
00:06:20,556 --> 00:06:25,026
<font color="#00ff00">Hujan, angin, salah satu sayap jatuh.
Semua orang dialihkan.</font>

34
00:06:25,028 --> 00:06:27,460
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Aku tahu, hidup tidak adil.</i></font>

35
00:06:29,597 --> 00:06:32,465
<font color="#00ff00">Mobil limomu bisa saja tabrakan.
/ Kau benar. Masih ada harapan.</font>

36
00:06:32,967 --> 00:06:36,570
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Setelah bertahun-tahun mungkin pianonya
tidak selaras, mereka harus menjadwal ulang.</i></font>

37
00:06:36,871 --> 00:06:39,104
<font color="#00ff00">Atau aku hanya tinggal mengambil
alat pengelas dan mengelas pianonya.</font>

38
00:06:39,106 --> 00:06:41,173
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Atau kau bisa membatalkannya.</i></font>

39
00:06:42,542 --> 00:06:44,910
<font color="#00ff00">Tunggu.
Apa maksudmu, mobil limo?</font>

40
00:06:45,178 --> 00:06:46,278
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Kukira kau yang menjemputku.</i></font>

41
00:06:46,280 --> 00:06:50,815
<font color="#00ff00">Tidak, aku di hotel.
Aku masih ada konferensi pers. Ingat?</font>

42
00:06:50,817 --> 00:06:54,752
<font color="#00ff00">Kau tak lihat ada seorang pria memegang
namamu? Aku meninggalkan pesan suara.</font>

43
00:06:54,754 --> 00:06:57,721
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Maksudmu orang asing menjemputku?
Apa yang terjadi dengan...?</i></font>

44
00:06:57,723 --> 00:07:00,691
<font color="#00ff00">Ashley dan Wayne bertemu aku di sini.</font>

45
00:07:00,693 --> 00:07:03,334
<font color="#00ff00">Sebenarnya, mereka ada di lantai bawah.
Kau ingin menyapanya?</font>

46
00:07:03,461 --> 00:07:06,830
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Kau bercanda? Mereka mungkin tak tahu
apa itu konser klasik.</i></font>

47
00:07:07,397 --> 00:07:10,266
<font color="#00ff00">Kau bisa jelaskan sendiri pada mereka
saat bertemu mereka.</font>

48
00:07:10,268 --> 00:07:11,534
<font color="#00ff00">Ah, tembak aku.</font>

49
00:07:12,436 --> 00:07:15,271
<font color="#00ff00">Sampaikan salamku pada mereka,
terima kasih untuk datang, semua itu.</font>

50
00:07:15,739 --> 00:07:19,074
<font color="#00ff00">Astaga, aku ragu mereka akan bisa
melalui seluruh acaranya.</font>

51
00:07:19,076 --> 00:07:20,275
<font color="#00ff00">Ayolah.
/ Apa?</font>

52
00:07:20,277 --> 00:07:24,613
<font color="#00ff00">Agensiku tak berhasil dapatkan kursi balkon.
Ashley akan melemparnya.</font>

53
00:07:25,781 --> 00:07:27,982
<font color="#00ff00">Aku harus pergi sekarang, jadi...</font>

54
00:07:27,984 --> 00:07:29,183
<font color="#00ff00">Tidak, tak perlu.
Terima kasih.</font>

55
00:07:29,185 --> 00:07:31,051
<font color="#00ff00">Tunggu sebentar, oke?</font>

56
00:07:31,053 --> 00:07:31,886
<font color="#00ff00">Hai!</font>

57
00:07:32,520 --> 00:07:34,321
<font color="#00ff00">Dia ingin bicara denganmu.</font>

58
00:07:34,323 --> 00:07:35,890
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Hey!
Emma!</i></font>

59
00:07:35,892 --> 00:07:37,690
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Hai.
Emma!</i></font>

60
00:07:38,692 --> 00:07:41,327
<font color="#00ff00">Astaga.
Kau tampak seksi!</font>

61
00:07:41,329 --> 00:07:43,396
<font color="#00ff00">Terima kasih.
Kau juga terlihat cantik.</font>

62
00:07:43,400 --> 00:07:44,890
<font color="#00ff00">Hai Ray. /
Sedang menelpon siapa.</font>

63
00:07:44,899 --> 00:07:46,332
<font color="#00ff00">Jangan membuatku bicara ditelepon dengan dia.</font>

64
00:07:46,334 --> 00:07:49,301
<font color="#00ff00">Ini hanya urusan kerjaan.
/ Oh, bagus.</font>

65
00:07:49,903 --> 00:07:51,970
<font color="#00ff00">Jadi apa kesepakatannya?
Apa dia datang ke sini?</font>

66
00:07:52,238 --> 00:07:56,875
<font color="#00ff00">Karena aku tahu bartender di Fridos
dan diskonnya 50 %.</font>

67
00:07:57,309 --> 00:07:59,977
<font color="#00ff00">Tom harus langsung ke teater.</font>

68
00:08:00,245 --> 00:08:03,681
<font color="#00ff00">Bagaimana dengan kesenangan sebelum acaranya?
/ Ini konser klasik, Ash.</font>

69
00:08:04,449 --> 00:08:07,384
<font color="#00ff00">Jadi artinya lebih baik jika Tom tidak mabuk.</font>

70
00:08:08,686 --> 00:08:10,620
<font color="#00ff00">Kita bisa berpesta setelahnya. Ya?</font>

71
00:08:10,888 --> 00:08:12,088
<font color="#00ff00">Tunggu, sebentar.</font>

72
00:08:12,323 --> 00:08:14,524
<font color="#00ff00">Aku punya sesuatu untukmu.
Aku membungkusnya dalam tasmu.</font>

73
00:08:14,792 --> 00:08:15,659
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Apa?</i></font>

74
00:08:15,661 --> 00:08:19,695
<font color="#00ff00">Hanya hadiah kecil. selamat datang
ke abad 21.</font>

75
00:08:20,064 --> 00:08:21,635
<font color="#00ff00">Katakan lagi, kenapa kau melakukan semua ini?</font>

76
00:08:21,670 --> 00:08:24,199
<font color="#00ff00">Karena sudah waktunya kau kembali
ke atas panggung.</font>

77
00:08:24,201 --> 00:08:25,301
<font color="#00ff00">Tunggu sebentar.</font>

78
00:08:25,326 --> 00:08:26,526
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Tolong lihat ke sini!</i></font>

79
00:08:28,200 --> 00:08:29,600
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Kau cantik sekali!</i></font>

80
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:32,400
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Ke arah sini!
/ Ke sebelah kanan!</i></font>

81
00:08:35,800 --> 00:08:36,700
<font color="#00ff00">Terima kasih.</font>

82
00:08:37,079 --> 00:08:38,812
<font color="#00ff00">Hei, kau masih di situ?
/ Ya.</font>

83
00:08:39,113 --> 00:08:41,648
<font color="#00ff00">Apa kau memakai tuksedo?
/ Haruskah?</font>

84
00:08:41,916 --> 00:08:43,583
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Kau terlambat, Tom.</i></font>

85
00:08:43,885 --> 00:08:47,054
<font color="#00ff00">Tak perlu ke hotel dan langsung saja
ke auditorium, oke?</font>

86
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:48,200
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Ya.</i></font>

87
00:08:48,522 --> 00:08:50,222
<font color="#00ff00">Kau sedang menggigit kukumu?</font>

88
00:08:51,124 --> 00:08:52,191
<font color="#00ff00">Tidak.</font>

89
00:08:53,226 --> 00:08:54,493
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Aku mencintaimu.</i></font>

90
00:08:54,728 --> 00:08:56,028
<font color="#00ff00">Aku juga.</font>

91
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:09,000
<font color="#00ff00">Taxi!</font>

92
00:09:15,046 --> 00:09:17,481
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Ke mana kita, Pak?</i></font>

93
00:09:37,233 --> 00:09:39,900
<font color="#00ff00">Abad ke 21...
/ Maaf, apa Pak?</font>

94
00:09:40,802 --> 00:09:41,802
<font color="#00ff00">Tidak.</font>

95
00:09:42,037 --> 00:09:43,337
<font color="#00ff00">Maaf.</font>

96
00:10:01,321 --> 00:10:02,721
<font color="#00ff00">Halo? /
Tom Selznick?</font>

97
00:10:03,390 --> 00:10:04,723
<font color="#00ff00">Mark dari A & V.
/ Hai, Mark.</font>

98
00:10:04,725 --> 00:10:09,027
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Ketika Marjorie berkata : "Tom, apa yang ada
di pikiranmu sekarang?", itulah isyaratmu.</i></font>

99
00:10:09,029 --> 00:10:10,328
<font color="#00ff00">Kau mengerti? /
Ya, kupikir begitu.</font>

100
00:10:10,362 --> 00:10:12,330
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Bagus. Oke, tunggu sebentar.</i></font>

101
00:10:13,265 --> 00:10:15,767
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Tiga, dua, satu...</i></font>

102
00:10:16,568 --> 00:10:20,203
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Jadi kau tak mengkonfirmasikan
rumor semalam?</i></font>

103
00:10:20,471 --> 00:10:23,373
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Aku melakukan audisi.
Aku tak bisa katakan lebih dari itu.</i></font>

104
00:10:23,741 --> 00:10:26,209
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Emma Selznick masih ikuti audisi?</i></font>

105
00:10:26,477 --> 00:10:28,444
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Ketika masuk ke film musikal, kurasa.</i></font>

106
00:10:29,179 --> 00:10:32,448
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Jadi kita akan mendengarmu menyanyi
untuk pertama kalinya?</i></font>

107
00:10:32,682 --> 00:10:35,117
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Oh ayolah, aku sudah banyak bicara.</i></font>

108
00:10:35,419 --> 00:10:39,020
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Aku bernyanyi sepanjang waktu. Di rumah,
di kamar mandi. Tanya saja suamiku!</i></font>

109
00:10:39,488 --> 00:10:42,724
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Pada kenyataannya, kita memang harus
menghadirkan si pria luar biasa.</i></font>

110
00:10:43,192 --> 00:10:46,528
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Terima kasih untuk waktumu.
Selalu menyenangkan bicara denganmu, Emma.</i></font>

111
00:10:46,921 --> 00:10:48,002
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Terima kasih.</i></font>

112
00:10:48,037 --> 00:10:51,565
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Tom Selznick, pianis paling bersinar
dari generasinya...</i></font>

113
00:10:51,567 --> 00:10:55,335
<font color="#00ff00"><i>... yang menikah dengan film paling bersinar
dari generasinya, sudah kembali.</i></font>

114
00:10:55,337 --> 00:10:58,137
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Sudah 5 tahun sejak dia pensiun dari panggung,</i></font>

115
00:10:58,139 --> 00:11:01,974
<font color="#00ff00"><i>tapi dalam hitungan menit, cuti panjang ini
akan menjadi sejarah.</i></font>

116
00:11:01,976 --> 00:11:05,945
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Harus kuakui aku tak ingin berada
dalam posisi Tom malam ini.</i></font>

117
00:11:05,947 --> 00:11:07,847
<font color="#00ff00">Tom, bagaimana kabarmu?
/ Halo?</font>

118
00:11:08,114 --> 00:11:11,983
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Tom, apa yang ada dalam pikiranmu sekarang?</i></font>

119
00:11:12,251 --> 00:11:14,186
<font color="#00ff00">Apa kau gugup?
/ Apa?</font>

120
00:11:14,487 --> 00:11:17,055
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Kau akan berkolaborasi dengan
F.C.O Philharmonic</i></font>

121
00:11:17,323 --> 00:11:20,624
<font color="#00ff00"><i>untuk bermain beberapa
potongan yang sangat sulit.</i></font>

122
00:11:21,059 --> 00:11:23,761
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Kau pasti mengalami malam yang buruk
akhir-akhir ini.</i></font>

123
00:11:23,763 --> 00:11:24,795
<font color="#00ff00">Tidak.</font>

124
00:11:24,920 --> 00:11:26,720
<font color="#00ff00">Kau tampak percaya diri sekali.
/ Ya.</font>

125
00:11:26,765 --> 00:11:30,667
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Benar. Dan piano apa tepatnya yang
akan kaumainkan malam ini?</i></font>

126
00:11:30,669 --> 00:11:32,469
<font color="#00ff00">Patrick piano.
/ Benar.</font>

127
00:11:32,703 --> 00:11:36,039
<font color="#00ff00">Aku menghabiskan berbulan-bulan,
tahunan, berlatih dengannya, jadi...</font>

128
00:11:36,307 --> 00:11:38,340
<font color="#00ff00">Ya. /
Di dalam ingatannya yang aku...</font>

129
00:11:38,608 --> 00:11:41,043
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Patrick Godureaux.
Pendengar kami mungkin mengenalnya</i></font>

130
00:11:41,544 --> 00:11:45,681
<font color="#00ff00"><i>sebagai raja musik eksentrik yang
kehilangan kekayaan keluarga, tapi...</i></font>

131
00:11:46,116 --> 00:11:49,450
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Bagiku dia lebih dari itu.
Dia juga seorang mentor.</i></font>

132
00:11:49,451 --> 00:11:53,121
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Yang kumaksud yaitu, apa
pentingnya piano bagimu?</i></font>

133
00:11:53,388 --> 00:11:56,457
<font color="#00ff00">Apa maksudmu?
/ "La Cinquette".</font>

134
00:11:56,892 --> 00:11:59,326
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Bagian yang tak bisa dimainkan, benar kan?</i></font>

135
00:11:59,427 --> 00:12:02,929
<font color="#00ff00"><i>"La Cinquette".
Apa aku salah mengucapkannya?</i></font>

136
00:12:03,197 --> 00:12:06,233
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Maksudku, kau memiliki sejarah
dengan bagian ini.</i></font>

137
00:12:06,534 --> 00:12:08,068
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Lima tahun lalu,
di Flannery...</i></font>

138
00:12:08,335 --> 00:12:10,569
<font color="#00ff00">Itu tak benar-benar berhasil.
/ Benar.</font>

139
00:12:10,571 --> 00:12:11,937
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Jadi pertanyaanku yaitu ini.</i></font>

140
00:12:12,405 --> 00:12:15,674
<font color="#00ff00">Kau kembali ke panggung setelah
bertahun-tahun diam.</font>

141
00:12:16,109 --> 00:12:18,244
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Apa kau gugup bermain piano yang sama?</i></font>

142
00:12:18,544 --> 00:12:21,279
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Apa kau gugup takut tersedak lagi?</i>
/ Tersedak?</font>

143
00:12:21,580 --> 00:12:25,016
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Apa kau melihat ini sebagai kesempatan
menebus kegagalan yang terakhir,</i></font>

144
00:12:25,284 --> 00:12:27,852
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Percobaanmu untuk selamanya...?</i>
/ Hentikan!</font>

145
00:12:29,187 --> 00:12:31,321
<font color="#00ff00">Maaf. Dengar...</font>

146
00:12:32,790 --> 00:12:33,657
<font color="#00ff00">Aku bermain piano.</font>

147
00:12:33,659 --> 00:12:36,927
<font color="#00ff00">Ini hanya pertunjukan lain,
tak ada yang lain.</font>

148
00:12:37,395 --> 00:12:40,930
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Baiklah, Tn. Selznick.
Untuk itu semua bincang-bincang kita.</i></font>

149
00:12:40,932 --> 00:12:42,632
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Semoga pertunjukkannya sukses!</i></font>

150
00:12:43,100 --> 00:12:45,201
<font color="#00ff00">Oh, tembak saja aku.</font>

151
00:13:07,656 --> 00:13:10,690
<font color="#00ff00">Pak, apa kau bisa memutar ke pintu belakang?</font>

152
00:13:10,692 --> 00:13:12,592
<font color="#00ff00">Bisa Pak. /
Terima kasih.</font>

153
00:13:36,782 --> 00:13:38,549
<font color="#00ff00">Maaf. /
Tak apa.</font>

154
00:13:39,183 --> 00:13:41,551
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Permisi, kau Tom Selznick?</i></font>

155
00:13:41,986 --> 00:13:43,053
<font color="#00ff00">Ya.</font>

156
00:13:43,055 --> 00:13:44,521
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Semoga sukses pertunjukkannya!</i></font>

157
00:13:44,523 --> 00:13:45,589
<font color="#00ff00">Terima kasih.</font>

158
00:14:01,103 --> 00:14:02,403
<font color="#00ff00">Selznick!</font>

159
00:14:02,671 --> 00:14:03,938
<font color="#00ff00">Selamat datang kembali.</font>

160
00:14:08,277 --> 00:14:10,410
<font color="#00ff00">Hei, Tommy. Pertunjukkan yang besar.</font>

161
00:14:10,678 --> 00:14:12,679
<font color="#00ff00">Terima kasih. Kau tampak sehat.</font>

162
00:14:12,880 --> 00:14:14,615
<font color="#00ff00">Ya. Baru bercerai!</font>

163
00:14:15,883 --> 00:14:17,284
<font color="#00ff00">Tom! Kau masih hidup!</font>

164
00:14:17,552 --> 00:14:19,885
