490
00:45:15,424 --> 00:45:16,589
<font color="#00ff00">Apa?</font>

491
00:45:16,857 --> 00:45:18,724
<font color="#00ff00"><i>" La Cinquette".</i></font>

492
00:45:19,459 --> 00:45:21,160
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Ingat itu?</i></font>

493
00:45:21,261 --> 00:45:22,328
<font color="#00ff00">Ada apa dengan itu?</font>

494
00:45:22,330 --> 00:45:27,699
<font color="#00ff00"><i>"The Unplayable Piece". Kecuali ada
