502
00:45:47,151 --> 00:45:48,952
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Kenapa? Karena kau membeku?</i></font>

503
00:45:49,420 --> 00:45:52,322
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Karena kau belum pernah setakut seperti
