508
00:46:06,268 --> 00:46:09,837
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Lebih dari Emma.</i></font>

509
00:46:10,272 --> 00:46:12,840
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Memegang tanganmu, mengantarmu
