532
00:47:52,631 --> 00:47:53,697
<font color="#00ff00">Wayne?</font>

533
00:48:02,773 --> 00:48:03,940
<font color="#00ff00">Wayne?</font>

534
00:48:08,945 --> 00:48:10,279
<font color="#00ff00">Astaga!</font>

535
00:48:10,647 --> 00:48:11,380
<font color="#00ff00">Maaf.</font>

536
00:48:11,382 --> 00:48:14,783
<font color="#00ff00">Tak apa. aku bingung sewaktu di sini.</font>

537
00:48:14,785 --> 00:48:16,251
<font color="#00ff00">Akan kuambilkan.
