538
00:49:05,597 --> 00:49:07,363
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Apa yang kau tunggu?</i></font>

539
00:49:12,836 --> 00:49:15,204
<font color="#00ff00">Ke mana aku harus pergi?
/ <i>Tangga.</i></font>

540
00:49:15,206 --> 00:49:17,005
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Belok kiri di bagian bawah.</i></font>

541
00:49:18,407 --> 00:49:20,876
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Tom, tangganya.</i></font>

542
00:49:25,181 --> 00:49:26,448
<font color="#00ff00"><i>3 pintu bawah.</i></font>

543
00:49:26,681 --> 00:49:29,216
<font color="#00ff00">Tunggu, apa?
Di mana?</font>

544
00:49:30,051 --> 00:49:31,652
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Ke kiri terus ke kiri lagi.</i></font>

545
00:49:44,198 --> 00:49:46,633
<font color="#00ff00">Permisi! Pak! Tunggu!</font>

546
00:49:46,900 --> 00:49:49,701
<font color="#00ff00">Tunggu! Tidak, tidak!</font>

547
00:49:52,372 --> 00:49:54,406
<font color="#00ff00">Hei, ada apa?</font>

548
00:49:54,408 --> 00:49:55,774
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Ada apa?</i></font>

549
00:49:56,042 --> 00:49:58,442
<font color="#00ff00">Dia membakar lembarannya.
/ <i>Sayang sekali.</i></font>

550
00:49:58,444 --> 00:50:00,645
<font color="#00ff00">Tunggu! Aku punya salinannya di rumah.</font>

551
00:50:00,913 --> 00:50:02,914
<font color="#00ff00">Aku bisa menyuruh seseorang mengambilnya.</font>

552
00:50:03,215 --> 00:50:05,750
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Kupikir kau tahu apa artinya ini.</i>
/ Tunggu!</font>

553
00:50:09,287 --> 00:50:11,054
<font color="#00ff00">Tunggu. Aku punya ide.</font>

554
00:50:20,397 --> 00:50:24,667
<font color="#00ff00">Apa ada masalah? / Tak apa-apa,
