559
00:50:37,178 --> 00:50:40,547
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Pergi ke ruang ganti dan jangan biarkan dia
lolos dari pengawasanmu.</i></font>

560
00:50:40,549 --> 00:50:41,815
<font color="#00ff00">Aku segera ke sana.</font>

561
00:50:47,120 --> 00:50:50,056
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Aku suka gaunmu.
Kau mengkilap.</i></font>

562
00:50:51,425 --> 00:50:53,426
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Emma? Sebelah sini.</i></font>

563
00:50:58,431 --> 00:51:00,332
<font color="#00ff00">Permisi. Terima kasih.</font>

564
00:51:02,902 --> 00:51:04,903
<font color="#00ff00">Kuharap kau menikmatinya.</font>

565
00:51:05,671 --> 00:51:08,372
<font color="#00ff00">Emma, ​​foto kau dan aku, kumohon.</font>

566
00:51:49,176 --> 00:51:51,745
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Apa kau mengawasi dia?
Jangan bilang kau sudah kehilangan dia.</i></font>

567
00:51:52,046 --> 00:51:54,047
<font color="#00ff00">Tidak, aku mengawasinya.</font>

568
00:51:54,548 --> 00:51:57,349
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Hati-hati. Emma meninggalkan teater.</i>
/ Dan?</font>

569
00:51:57,617 --> 00:52:00,252
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Ikuti dia.</i> / Aku tak bisa berada
di dua tempat sekaligus.</font>

570
00:52:18,536 --> 00:52:21,438
<font color="#00ff00">Jadi, kauingin aku melakukan apa?</font>

571
00:52:21,440 --> 00:52:22,739
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Susul dia.</i></font>

572
00:52:23,574 --> 00:52:25,175
<font color="#00ff00">"Susul dia."</font>

573
00:52:26,110 --> 00:52:30,246
<font color="#00ff00">Permintaanmu adalah perintahku...
Brengsek.</font>

