00:52:33,817 --> 00:52:36,285
<font color="#00ff00">Ny. Selznick! Ny. Selznick...</font>

575
00:52:38,587 --> 00:52:40,088
<font color="#00ff00">Tanya dia.</font>

576
00:52:40,956 --> 00:52:43,658
<font color="#00ff00">Boleh aku berfoto bersama Anda?</font>

577
00:52:53,501 --> 00:52:55,169
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Para hadirin,</i></font>

578
00:52:55,570 --> 00:52:58,471
<font color="#00ff00"><i>pastikan ponsel anda dalam posisi "silent".</i></font>

579
00:53:00,741 --> 00:53:05,011
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Para hadirin, kami mohon
pastikan ponsel Anda...</i></font>

580
00:53:05,279 --> 00:53:06,813
<font color="#00ff00"><i>...dalam posisi "silent".</i></font>

581
00:53:11,517 --> 00:53:12,651
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Sayang?</i></font>

582
00:53:13,853 --> 00:53:14,786
<font color="#00ff00">Emma!</font>

583
00:53:14,788 --> 00:53:18,356
<font color="#00ff00">Saya harap kami tak mengganggu, Tn. Selznick.
Dia memaksa.</font>

584
00:53:18,358 --> 00:53:20,358
<font color="#00ff00">Aku tak bermaksud membuat masalah./
Oh, tidak.</font>

585
00:53:20,360 --> 00:53:23,027
<font color="#00ff00">Tak setiap hari aku mendapat
2 selebriti sekaligus untuk ditangani.</font>

586
00:53:23,762 --> 00:53:25,996
<font color="#00ff00">Dia seperti penyelamat
yang membawaku ke sini.</font>

587
00:53:26,498 --> 00:53:27,688
<font color="#00ff00">Dia berarti.</font>

588
00:53:27,723 --> 00:53:31,134
<font color="#00ff00">Aku datang hanya ingin mengatakan
sungguh pekerjaan bagus yang kaulakukan.</font>

589
00:53:31,136 --> 00:53:33,636
<font color="#00ff00">Sungguh, kau bermain begitu indah.</font>

590
00:53:43,546 --> 00:53:45,614
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Para hadirin...</i></font>

591
00:53:46,082 --> 00:53:47,416
<font color="#00ff00">Kita harus pergi.</font>

592
00:53:47,916 --> 00:53:50,685
<font color="#00ff00">Mungkin kita harus meninggalkanmu sendirian.
Tapi aku...</font>

593
00:53:52,654 --> 00:53:54,489
<font color="#00ff00">Aku menyayangimu, sayang.</font>

594
00:53:55,858 --> 00:53:58,825
<font color="#00ff00">Sampai jumpa di atas panggung, Tn. Selznick.</font>

595
00:53:59,761 --> 00:54:00,994
<font color="#00ff00">Ijinkan aku mengantarmu.</font>

596
00:54:00,996 --> 00:54:04,865
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Pertunjukkan malam ini akan dilanjutkan
dalam 5 menit lagi.</i></font>

597
00:54:06,225 --> 00:54:11,837
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Dengan hormat kami meminta anda
untuk kembali ke kursi anda saat ini.</i></font>

598
00:54:16,977 --> 00:54:18,843
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Terima kasih banyak.</i></font>

599
00:54:21,247 --> 00:54:23,281
<font color="#00ff00">Hampir saja.</font>

600
00:54:24,984 --> 00:54:26,251
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Sama-sama.</i></font>

601
00:54:26,786 --> 00:54:28,218
<font color="#00ff00">Lagi pula, itu akan sia-sia.</font>

602
00:54:28,220 --> 00:54:32,222
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Tenang. Itulah yang selalu mereka
