620
00:55:22,869 --> 00:55:25,871
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Itu maksud pembicaraanmu, benar kan?</i></font>

621
00:55:26,201 --> 00:55:27,331
<font color="#00ff00"><i>Karena...</i></font>

622
00:55:27,366 --> 00:55:30,641
<font color="#00ff00"><i>...bagaimanapun kau mengukir sejarah.
